    "When these drivers interact with each other, perhaps compounding or cascading, vulnerability should be treated as a multi-layered condition (Luna, 2019): e.g., the compound of ethnicity and socio-economic conditions often leads to a heightened sensitivity to the biases of prediction systems.",
